        <updateDate>2021-07-07T14:31:03Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Upskilling and Retraining Assistance Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases to $12,000 in 2021-2022, the exclusion from employee gross income, for income tax purposes, of employer-paid educational assistance programs. </p> <p>The bill also expands the exclusion to include amounts paid for education-related tools and technology (e.g., hand tools, computers, software, licensure fees).</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
